#!/home/martink/bin/perl

=pod

=head1 NAME

generatetriads - generates all letter groups of a given size

=head1 SYNOPSIS

  generatetriads [-n GROUPSIZE]

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Generates all combinations of GROUPSIZE letters.

=head1 OPTIONS

=head2 -n GROUPSIZE

Set the number of letters with -n. By default, n=3 (triads).

=head1 AUTHOR

Martin Krzywinski

=head1 CONTACT

  Martin Krzywinski
  Genome Sciences Centre
  Vancouver BC Canada
  www.bcgsc.ca
  martink@bcgsc.ca

=cut

